race_comments: Johnny Sauter won the NextEra Energy Resources 250 at Daytona International Speedway, his 18th NASCAR Camping World Truck Series win. Prior to the start of the race, the following trucks dropped to the rear of the field under penalty: Nos. 3, 7, 39, 75 (unapproved adjustments).
